OOC: You've got Menasor this time Jer =)

--- Dead-End / Drag Strip ---

Dead-End and Drag Strip cheer, then transform into their vehicle 
modes, to form their pieces of Menasor. 


On 24 Jun 2001, at 11:45, robertdahl wrote:

> The chant cut straight into Motormaster fuel pump. All his confusion
> washed away, by his passion, in the cause he believed so strongly in.
> He may have been created by Decepticons, but he served because he
> believed in it. He transformed, stood up, and held out his hand, and
> followed the mantra. How he would make Slaughter pay, for making him
> forget that. "You heard Megatron boys, Transform to form MENASOR." he
> said transforming to his truck mode again. Speedbreaker emerged from
> the woods, and joined the three transformed Stunticons.
